{"body": "I'd still like this when the server is starting, but in a second thought, what if the user rolls back? the schema wouldn't be up to date and the server wouldn't start, that might not be ok, so we could add an option to the configuration (and configure in config/development.rb), something like this:\n    \n    $ rails server\n    You have pending migrations.\n    Try running 'bundle exec rake db:migrate' or use config.whatever_the_name_config_option_is = false\n\nThere's another thing, `needs_migration?` would be better to me if it were `pending_migrations?`", "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rails/rails/issues/comments/5770170", "created_at": "2012-05-17T18:09:02Z", "html_url": "https://github.com/rails/rails/pull/4165#issuecomment-5770170", "updated_at": "2012-05-17T18:09:02Z", "repo": "rails", "issue_id": 4165, "user": {"following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/rafmagana/following{/other_user}", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/rafmagana/events{/privacy}", "organizations_url": "https://api.github.com/users/rafmagana/orgs", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/rafmagana", "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/rafmagana/gists{/gist_id}", "html_url": "https://github.com/rafmagana", "subscriptions_url": "https://api.github.com/users/rafmagana/subscriptions", "avatar_url": "https://2.gravatar.com/avatar/40bd727b22d74930f292b63d45a71b07?d=https%3A%2F%2Fidenticons.github.com%2F17cf4f4b757e960792210cfcedb91d39.png", "repos_url": "https://api.github.com/users/rafmagana/repos", "received_events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/rafmagana/received_events", "gravatar_id": "40bd727b22d74930f292b63d45a71b07", "starred_url": "https://api.github.com/users/rafmagana/starred{/owner}{/repo}", "login": "rafmagana", "type": "User", "id": 92894, "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/rafmagana/followers"}, "owner": "rails", "_id": {"$oid": "52382bb5bd3543c15100f153"}, "id": 5770170, "issue_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rails/rails/issu